apifyData.description: Located between Floors 26 & 27 of Cond. Plaza La Inmaculada I, this 2-story corner Penthouse gem possesses the best views of San Juan, with a 360-degree skyline view of San Juan Bay, El Yunque Mountains, the city, and more. The Penthouse consists of approximately 2,600 sq. ft. with 2 floors featuring custom-built finishings and design. Level 1 includes the kitchen, dining, and living rooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2 bedrooms. Level 2 consists of the master bedroom with a custom-designed bathroom and 2 walk-in closets. Additionally, this 2nd level includes an ample terrace area with unobstructed views of the entire metro area, with an option to create a mini-bar, perfect for hosting or relaxing at sunset, and a half-bathroom. The Penthouse includes 2 covered parking spaces and a 24/7 security gate community entrance.
